OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FThe SNP's manifesto for next month's
OL,7,FHolyrood election will be "bursting
OL,8,Fwith ambition", while also setting out
OL,9,Fpolitics to help Scots "struggling"
OL,10,Famid the cost-of-living crisis, John
OL,11,FSwinney has said.
OL,13,FWith just over three weeks to go until
OL,14,FScots go to the polls, the First
OL,15,FMinister is due to unveil his party's
OL,16,Fpackage of policy proposals on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,26,@oD@[OUpD@NO]qD@XOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
