CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FWith the SNP leader saying that
OL,7,F"people are really struggling at the
OL,8,Fmoment", he vowed the manifesto would
OL,9,Fhave "supporting people with the cost
OL,10,Fof living at its heart".
OL,12,FThe commitment came as he accused the
OL,13,FLabour Government at Westminster of
OL,14,F"not lifting a finger" to help Scots
OL,15,Fin need.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@GO]qD@FOUrD@WO]vD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
