OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FMr Swinney, speaking ahead of a
OL,7,Fcampaign visit to Maybole in Ayrshire
OL,8,Fon Wednesday, said: "People are really
OL,9,Fstruggling at the moment ` bills just
OL,10,Fkeep going up, food prices are
OL,11,Fextortionate and the prices at the
OL,12,Fpumps are through the roof.
OL,14,F"Meanwhile, Keir Starmer and the UK
OL,15,FLabour Government are not lifting a
OL,16,Ffinger to help.
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,F"Well, my message is clear ` if the UK
OL,7,FLabour Government are not going to act
OL,8,Fto bring bills down, they should get
OL,9,Fout of the road for an SNP Government
OL,10,Fthat will."
OL,12,FThe First Minister said: "Where we
OL,13,Fhave the powers in Scotland, we will
OL,14,Fact ` building on the support we
OL,15,Falready have in place to support
OL,16,Fpeople with the cost of living
OL,17,Fincluding abolishing peak rail fares,
OL,18,Fextending childcare provision and
OL,19,Fensuring most people in Scotland pay
OL,20,Fless income tax than south of the
OL,21,Fborder. "
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]tD@ZOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
