OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FAs well as helping people with the
OL,7,Fcost-of-living crisis, Mr Swinney said
OL,8,Fthat his party's manifesto "will be
OL,9,Fbursting with ambition for Scotland's
OL,10,Ffuture".
OL,12,FThis, he said was "because the SNP is
OL,13,Fon Scotland's side" with the First
OL,14,FMinister asking Scots to give his
OL,15,Fparty a majority at Holyrood.
OL,17,FThis he said would allow them to
OL,18,F"improve the NHS, support people with
OL,19,Fthe cost of living" but also to
OL,20,F"deliver the fresh start of
OL,21,Findependence".
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@GO]tD@SOUuD@SO]zD@AOU{D@SO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
