CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FScottish Greens, however, urged the
OL,7,FSNP leader to "drop the pretence" that
OL,8,Fonly an SNP majority can deliver a
OL,9,Ffresh vote on the future of the UK.
OL,11,FParty co-leader Gillian Mackay
OL,12,Finsisted: "Independence is much bigger
OL,13,Fthan any party, and we need to work
OL,14,Ftogether to deliver it.
OL,16,F"It's time for John Swinney to level
OL,17,Fwith people and stop pretending that
OL,18,Fit is only SNP MSPs that count."
OL,26,@oD@OOUoD@aO]tD@KOUxD@AOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FShe added: "The stakes couldn't be
OL,7,Fhigher. With Keir Starmer's Labour
OL,8,FParty shedding trust and votes and the
OL,9,Fvery real prospect of Nigel Farage in
OL,10,FDowning Street, it has never been more
OL,11,Fcrucial for Scotland to choose our own
OL,12,Ffuture.
OL,14,F"The people of Scotland deserve so
OL,15,Fmuch better than what Labour is
OL,16,Foffering. Why should we be stuck with
OL,17,Fa Prime Minister so bad that even Anas
OL,18,FSarwar wants rid of him?"
OL,26,@nD@LOUvD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,FAdding that independence "is about
OL,7,Fdemocracy and the simple principle
OL,8,Fthat the best people to choose our own
OL,9,Ffuture are the people who live here",
OL,10,Fshe said that "poll after poll shows
OL,11,Fthat the only way to ensure a pro-
OL,12,Findependence majority in our
OL,13,FParliament is with a record vote for
OL,14,Fthe Scottish Greens".
OL,16,FMs Mackay said: "With the powers of a
OL,17,Fnormal, independent country, we could
OL,18,Ffinally move on from the broken
OL,19,Fpolitics of Westminster and do so much
OL,20,Fmore for our climate and our
OL,21,Fcommunities.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUqD@dO]rD@OOUvD@TO]xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
