OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776214384
OL,3,CSNP manifesto will be 'bursting with
OL,4,Cambition', pledges John Swinney
OL,6,F"Without a pro-independence majority
OL,7,Fthat opportunity will be taken off the
OL,8,Fagenda, possibly for good. We can't
OL,9,Frisk that."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@KO]
